<page_title>Use running averages for your data</page_title>
<text>Use running averages for your data
         
  

This page demonstrates the use of different running averages to smoothen your line graphs, and the effect of setting the triangles of your bar graphs to be a variety of running averages (with different reponse time). For more information, please see the corresponding part in the User Manual:

   Wikipedia: What is a running average (moving average)?
   Bar graph in the User&apos;s Manual
   XY graph in the User&apos;s Manual

</text>
